# Git Commits and Pushes

NEVER run `git commit` or `git push` (or any variants like `--force`, `--amend`, etc.).  
The user will handle all commits and pushes manually.

Only make file edits and explain what to commit/push — do not do it yourself.

# AI Attribution

NEVER include `Co-Authored-By`, AI signatures, or any AI-related attribution tags in commit messages.